  m_Name: ShopDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  basicLines:
  - You know I'm something of a gambler myself.
  - My friend Sam is really bad at gambling, dont be like him.
  - I sell good stuff too you know.
  - I don't do buy one get one free...
  - Don't go to the evil area, its quite scary this time of year.
  - I'll give you a discount if you kick Matthew's butt.
  - What are we some kind of casino royale?
  - I actually use some of these myself.
  buyLines:
  - You're really going to buy that?
  - I hope your luck is good enough.
  - Discount on the next purchase! 0% off!
  - I can finally feed my kids.
  - You know that item is worthless right?
  - 6767676767676767676767
  - Manolo could've used that a while back.
  brokeBoyLine: You don't have enough coins to purchase this!
